        <h1 class="fw-bold">Next Level Racing: Elevate Your Sim Racing Experience</h1>
        <p>Next Level Racing is one of the most recognized brands in the sim racing and flight simulation industries. Known for their high-quality cockpits, motion platforms, and accessories, Next Level Racing products cater to both casual racers and professional sim setups. With a focus on innovation, immersion, and ergonomics, they provide a true "next level" experience for every sim enthusiast.</p>
        <br>
        <hr>

        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Racing Cockpits for Every Level</h2>
        <p>Next Level Racing offers a wide range of racing cockpits, from beginner-friendly stands to fully adjustable professional-grade rigs.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>GTLite / F-GT Lite</strong> – Foldable, lightweight, and perfect for limited spaces</li>
            <li><strong>GTTrack</strong> – Heavy-duty frame designed for stability and compatibility with direct drive wheels</li>
            <li><strong>F-GT Elite</strong> – Premium aluminum profile cockpit with full GT and Formula position adjustability</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <hr>

        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Motion Platforms & Haptic Feedback</h2>
        <p>For racers and pilots who want full immersion, Next Level Racing offers motion solutions that transform your setup into a professional-grade simulator.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Motion Platform V3</strong> – Compact motion system that delivers pitch, roll, and vibration</li>
            <li><strong>Traction Plus</strong> – Adds yaw and surge for enhanced car motion realism</li>
            <li>Compatible with most racing games and flight sims</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <hr>

        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Flight Sim Gear</h2>
        <p>Next Level Racing is also a leader in flight simulation hardware, offering robust and modular flight cockpits.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Flight Simulator Lite</strong> – Foldable setup for casual pilots</li>
            <li><strong>Boeing-licensed flight cockpit</strong> – Realistic flight station with adjustable mounts</li>
            <li>Supports yokes, throttles, rudders, and HOTAS systems</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <hr>
            <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Adjustable Monitor Stands & Accessories</h2>
            <p>To complete the setup, Next Level Racing offers a full suite of accessories that improve ergonomics and visual immersion.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Single and triple monitor stands with height and angle adjustment</li>
                <li>Keyboard trays, mouse mounts, and motion adapters</li>
                <li>Seat add-ons and upgrades for comfort and positioning</li>
            </ul>
        <br>
        <hr>

        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Modular and Expandable</h2>
        <p>Most Next Level Racing gear is modular, meaning you can start small and expand over time as your needs grow.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Cockpits compatible with direct drive wheels, load cell pedals, and shifters</li>
            <li>Motion platforms that bolt directly into existing rigs</li>
            <li>Support for PC, PlayStation, and Xbox (depending on hardware)</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <hr>

        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Why Choose Next Level Racing?</h2>
        <p>Next Level Racing is a trusted name for both beginners and professionals. Their gear combines comfort, functionality, and performance—making them a top choice worldwide.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Innovative design and durable construction</li>
            <li>Excellent support for motion and multi-platform setups</li>
            <li>Used by esports teams, flight schools, and sim centers globally</li>
        </ul>
